{"tid":2118007,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華要求日禁漁船入釣島海域  日明確拒絕 加強戰機緊急升空標準","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T10:52:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bb4b53114cf0076c8fc614325ab3fad32207b9","tid":2118007,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200721/ZVII67TUCG3GXSR2ZN3U6IILRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200721%2FZVII67TUCG3GXSR2ZN3U6IILRQ%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1c%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=124c262d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200721%2FZVII67TUCG3GXSR2ZN3U6IILRQ%2F&h=cc857f34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200721/ZVII67TUCG3GXSR2ZN3U6IILRQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華要求日禁漁船入釣島海域 <br />\n日明確拒絕 加強戰機緊急升空標準<br />\n<br />\n日媒報道，北京政府近日罕有透過外交渠道，要求日本禁止日方漁船進入釣魚台（日稱尖閣諸島）附近海域，以及中止沖繩縣更改釣魚台行政區名措施，兩項要求均被日方明確拒絕。而隨着中日釣魚島爭議升溫，日本防衞省已進一步升級航空自衞隊的緊急升空標準。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美議員擬提案授權總統武力護台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GbMXnEIib4gAJgWhGFJUIT-7U1Y=/190x97/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4LQEN3DEZFQVRSIXTMWVHPELYA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGbMXnEIib4gAJgWhGFJUIT-7U1Y%3D%2F190x97%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4LQEN3DEZFQVRSIXTMWVHPELYA.gif&h=85e6ef57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中日釣魚台主權爭議再升溫。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，北京7月對日本政府主張擁有尖閣諸島的主權，通過外交渠道，以日本漁船在附近作業是「入侵領海」為由，要求禁止駛入。中國政府同時要求叫停沖繩縣石垣市議會。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華派海警船追蹤監視<br />\n<br />\n沖繩縣石垣市議會上月通過，將釣魚島所在行政區，從「登野城」改名為「登野城尖閣」，預計10月1日施行。共同社指出，中國正加派海警船隻駛入釣魚島附近、並追蹤監視日本漁船。兩艘海警船本月初曾駛入釣魚島並逗留39小時23分，創下2012年9月以來的最長記錄。<br />\n<br />\n除了向日本政府提出要求，近年中國在釣魚島動作多多，去年將浙江省的戰機升空基地，改到距釣魚台更近的福建省，配備殲-11等現代化戰機，意味中國可在20多分鐘飛抵釣魚台。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，以免讓解放軍戰機進入北緯25度至26度之間的釣魚島空域，日本航空自衞隊把北緯27度設為「防衞線」。但近年來，越過該線南下的中國軍機激增，防衞省將應對一。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QGpNiCn9IO9aDlWpnEPw3yOJJaQ=/524x328/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYLVH7JCKXOR54HQHIIJ4CLC2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQGpNiCn9IO9aDlWpnEPw3yOJJaQ%3D%2F524x328%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYLVH7JCKXOR54HQHIIJ4CLC2U.gif&h=20a1fd38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本F-15J戰機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GNR1-bmmoC7y_sjKZJm8wE7cvSA=/524x439/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OS57SJNEMYWBRZHND2VPDMRCRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGNR1-bmmoC7y_sjKZJm8wE7cvSA%3D%2F524x439%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOS57SJNEMYWBRZHND2VPDMRCRA.gif&h=01ec8bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中方不滿日本漁船駛入釣魚島海域。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xTqEg14Ake9BdLFT3nvD8R9ZIcg=/524x439/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MM7A6HQJRO5ONUPWYBJ7DFBO6A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxTqEg14Ake9BdLFT3nvD8R9ZIcg%3D%2F524x439%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMM7A6HQJRO5ONUPWYBJ7DFBO6A.gif&h=c3fbda71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石垣市議會上月通過議案，更改釣魚島的行政區名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逾六成人欲取消習訪日<br />\n<br />\n日本政府一名不願具名的中國問題專家指出，中國決心改變釣魚台周圍的現狀很明顯，並且是長期策略，指武漢肺炎疫情大流行對北京而言是一個機遇，因很多政府均沒有足夠資源作回擊。日本政府預期疫情減緩後，北京仍將繼續積極推動其領土主張，兩國軍事摩擦的可能性將升高。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日本經濟新聞發表最新民調顯示，有62%的日本受訪者認為「應該取消」邀請中國國家主席習近平以國賓身份訪日，回。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n共同社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HAtNpoZFYKWfnvJHupOdY04ycsA=/190x277/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BI5HRNHAPCJRLL7KMYV3XJDQK4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHAtNpoZFYKWfnvJHupOdY04ycsA%3D%2F190x277%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBI5HRNHAPCJRLL7KMYV3XJDQK4.gif&h=5ad22ede&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f4054219728364d8b36bab34d3b9c9f2b14b97e","tid":2118007,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:05:05.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2eb2c86624e96584cc93e8570889ad872efa100","tid":2118007,"uid":98139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:06:06.000Z","msg":"加速帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e93ae7e13ab38f0bde510138609a0cd18f58490","tid":2118007,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"點解佢自己唔派人守住領土？"},{"pid":"a785f4f7b3aa480a72bb8df304ffdd60d7b601a7","tid":2118007,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:48:13.000Z","msg":"起返個雷達站啦"},{"pid":"58adaf65480958d6420fb7bddf1c5e9f961d67fb","tid":2118007,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"四面樹敵八面威風"},{"pid":"dd0a858bea953ce581f42555a9800f3ecd927399","tid":2118007,"uid":62721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"日本：夠薑就埋黎搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}